# Indian Consumer Internet Alternative Data Tracker

Fully automated daily pipeline that scrapes and cleans real-time pricing, ratings, and availability data for 70+ Indian consumer brands (Swiggy, Zomato, Blinkit, Flipkart, Nykaa, etc.).

## Features
- Runs daily (or on demand)
- Tracks menu prices, discounts, ratings, delivery times, stock status
- Automatically flags anomalies (>10% price change, rating drops, out-of-stock alerts)
- Outputs clean CSV + investor-style one-page summary

## Tech Stack
Python • BeautifulSoup • pandas • Selenium • requests

